{"tid":1701303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"魯比奧將晤麥康奈爾商討香港人權與民主法案表決","createTime":"2019-11-09T03:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T07:45:29.000Z","uid":125168,"like":79,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"5cf96d267fa35ddb4f607411d3450798d73c97d0","tid":1701303,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:45:42.000Z","msg":"魯比奧將晤麥康奈爾商討香港人權與民主法案表決<br />\n<br />\n美國共和黨參議員魯比奧與參議院外交關係委員會主席里施，下星期將會與負責安排參議院表決議程的參議院多數黨領袖麥康奈爾會面，討論《香港人權與民主法案》在參議院全院表決的時間表。眾議院上月16日全院通過《香港人權與民主法案》，魯比奧原本預期，參議院可以在10月底前通過，但法案至今仍未排上參議院的表決議程，引發多名跨黨派議員不滿，矛頭指向麥康奈爾。有分析認為，麥康奈爾拖延法案表決，以便中美簽署貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n2019-11-09 11:35:56 <br />\n<br />\nSource: RTHK"},{"pid":"bbc3ae8c6897e867a8c43eae6337e2b58ccda8d0","tid":1701303,"uid":21545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:52:16.000Z","msg":"逼宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec912c06a3780c38b10bf91dab6feafa16afba3","tid":1701303,"uid":39234,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:54:10.000Z","msg":"Rubio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2761a7c2894187a84f4ac9a8c6b9986600f626","tid":1701303,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbb614a50c9970b5394c277dd1adcc89cdd8c22","tid":1701303,"uid":64743,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:55:03.000Z","msg":"Rubio <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e07a0c3743cf0e8bc64b1d7fb5fe592154180a","tid":1701303,"uid":225130,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"根本侵都係仆街黎<br />\n搵趙小蘭做交通部長就知咩事啦"},{"pid":"f03adc58d71909b2a2c646042a7c6441a411f9e9","tid":1